            <text>
                <body>
                    <div type="edition">
                        <div type="textpart">
                            <ab><persName><name ref="Iudo">Iudo</name></persName> filio bone memorie
                                <persName><name ref="Otto">Odi</name></persName> per il remedium
                        anime mee offre <rs key="#Churches">ecclesia</rs> et <rs key="#Monasteries"
                            >monasterio</rs>
                        <orgName key="#Churches #Monasteries" ref="#juridical_persons/79">Sancti
                            Petri</orgName> sito loco <placeName key="#Monasteries"
                            ref="#places/285">Palatiolo</placeName> prope <placeName
                            key="#Monasteries" ref="#places/85">Monte Virde</placeName>, idest una
                            <rs key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie">res</rs> mea illa quam abeo in loco
                            <placeName key="#Casae/cassinae_massaricie" ref="#places/289">Aqua
                            Calida</placeName>, con tutte le sue dipendenze. Pena del doppio. Chiede
                        a <persName key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name ref="Rodulfus"
                            >Rodulfo</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs> et <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> donni
                        imperatoris la stesura della cartula. Actuum <placeName ref="#places/285"
                            >loco intus monasterio Sancti Petri</placeName>. Testimoni: <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Hubertus">Uberti</name></persName> filio bone
                        memorie <persName><name ref="Hubertus">Uberti</name></persName>; <persName
                            key="#Witness"><name ref="Ildebrandinus">Ildibrandini</name></persName>
                        filio bone memorie <persName><name ref="Albertus">Alberti</name></persName>;
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Petrus">Petrus</name></persName>.
                        Scrive: Rodulfus notarius et iudex donni imperatoris.</ab>
                        </div>
                    </div>
